summary: An Ordinance appropriating money from the General Fund to pay the owner of Lot Twelve (12), Block Fifty-nine (59), Denny & Hoyt's Addition to the City of Seattle, for repairs to House No. 137 Dravus Street, occasioned by a slide, in the grading of Etrutia Street, et al, as provided for by Ordinance No. 12501, creating Local Improvement District No. 1095.
